{"word":"G5298 - ὑποχωρέω - hypochōréō - hoop-okh-o-reh'-o - Go aside","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποχωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypochōréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-okh-o-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go aside</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தனித்துப்போ, போ"},{"paragraph":"to go back to withdraw"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G5562 - χωρέω - chōréō - kho-reh'-o/5562\">G5562</a>; to <i>vacate down</i>, that is, <i>retire</i> quietly: - go aside, withdraw self.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}